import React from 'react';
import { Header, Button, Icon } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Nav = () => {
    return (
        <Header as='h2' floated='right'>
            Sage Jordan
            <Button basic color='red'>
                <Icon name='home' color='red' />
                Home
            </Button>
            <Button basic color='red'>
                <Icon disabled name='home' />
                About
            </Button>
            <Button basic color='red'>
                <Icon disabled name='home' />
                Projects
            </Button>
        </Header>
    )
}

export default Nav;
